<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_478_r1l19">Wır ~ dıe <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> etc . Bekennen etc Als vns dıe <expan>hochwırdıg<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_478_r1l20"><expan>durchleẅchtıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>fürſt<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> ʒu Maincʒ <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Ott ʒu Tryer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_478_r1l21"><expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>dıetr<ex>ich</ex></expan> ʒu Cöln Ercʒbıſchöffe <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>lud<ex>wig</ex></expan> <expan>pfallncʒgr<ex>af</ex></expan> bey Reyn etc <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_478_r1l22"><expan>albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> ʒu <expan>Sachſ<ex>en</ex></expan> etc vnd <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>Marggr<ex>af</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>Brandemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_478_r1l23">alle des <expan>heılıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Römıſche<ex>n</ex></expan> Reıchs <expan>kurfürſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> gnedıg <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> . <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_478_r1l24">als der <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan> durchleẅchtıgıſt fürſt vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ~ <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>Sıgmu<ex>n</ex>d</expan> . <expan>Römiſch<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_478_r1l25"><expan>Vng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd ʒu Beheim etc künıg . <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . <expan>Jr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_478_r1l26"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ den <expan>fürſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>graf<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>Rıtt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>knechte<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>Stette<ex>n</ex></expan> vormals </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_478_r1l27"><expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> tag geſecʒt hab gen <expan>Regenſp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> / Alſo hab ſıch Jr <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_478_r1l28">als ſıe <expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> ʒu Weſel beyein <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ſeyn / eins tags <expan>v<ex>er</ex>eynet</expan> ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_478_r1l29">vns gen <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> auf der <expan>heılıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ʒwölfpotte<ex>n</ex></expan> tag diuiſıo </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_479" id="238v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_479_r1l1">ʒu latein ſchıerıſt <expan>künft<ex>ig</ex></expan> wan ſıe bedunk daʒ <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> tag <expan>geleg<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd be= </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_479_r1l2">keͣmlıch bey vns ſey . Vnd wıe Jr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> Jr <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ʒu dem <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_479_r1l3"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ dem <expan>Römıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> etc künıg getan vnd <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>künıgl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_479_r1l4"><expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> den tag alſo <expan>v<ex>er</ex>kündet</expan> hab daʒ ſıe <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein <expan>künıgl<ex>ich</ex></expan> maıeſtat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_479_r1l5"><expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan> . Jn ſeinſelbs <expan>p<ex>er</ex>ſon</expan> ʒu <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> tag <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> . Vnd darauf <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_479_r1l6"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ den <expan>fürſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>graf<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>Stette<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> den tag auch alſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_479_r1l7"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>kündet</expan> vnd ſıe <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan> darcʒu <expan>ʒukome<ex>n</ex></expan> / Vnd als Jr <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_479_r1l8">darauf an vns <expan>geſunne<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan> hat / Jn vnd den Jren geleyt ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_479_r1l9">geben etc / Alſo geben wır den <expan>obg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ den <expan>kurfürſt<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_479_r1l10"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Otten vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dıetr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>Ercʒbıſchoff<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>lud<ex>wig</ex></expan> <expan>pfallncʒgr<ex>af</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_479_r1l11"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>Marggr<ex>af</ex></expan> etc Vnd Jr <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>graf<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_479_r1l12">Reͣten <expan>Rıtt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>knecht<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd den Jren vnd nemlıch <expan>alle<ex>n</ex></expan> den dıe ſıe mıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_479_r1l13">Jn auf dıe <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> ʒeıt gen <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> <expan>brınge<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> . auf <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> tag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_479_r1l14">vnd weıl <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> tag vnd teydıng wern vnd vıer tag darnach . bey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_479_r1l15">vns ʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> / ein ſlecht geleyt on <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> . Mıt <expan>vrk<ex>unde</ex></expan> dıcʒ <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_479_r1l16"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſıgelt</expan> mit <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> ʒuruck <expan>aufgedrukte<ex>n</ex></expan> Jnſıgel . Geben ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_478" id="238r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
