<div type="content">
<ab>Wir die <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> etc., bekennen
                                                etc., als uns die
                                                  <expan>hochwirdig<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>durchlewchtig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>fürst<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>,
                                                  <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> zu Maincz,
                                                  <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Ott zu Tryer,
                                                  <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Dietr<ex>ich</ex></expan> zu Cöln,
                                                erczbischöffe, <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Lud<ex>wig</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>pfallnczgr<ex>af</ex></expan> bey Reyn
                                                etc., <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan> zu
                                                  <expan>Sachs<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., und
                                                  <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>marggr<ex>af</ex></expan> zu
                                                  <expan>Brandemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> etc., alle des
                                                  <expan>heilig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>römische<ex>n</ex></expan> reichs
                                                  <expan>kurfürst<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> gnedig
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, als der
                                                  <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan> durchlewchtigist
                                                fürst und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>,
                                                  <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Sigmu<ex>n</ex>d</expan>,
                                                  <expan>römisch<ex>er</ex></expan>, zu
                                                  <expan>Ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und zu Beheim etc.
                                                künig, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>,
                                                  <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, den
                                                  <expan>fürst<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>graf<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>,
                                                  <expan>ritt<ex>er</ex>n</expan>,
                                                  <expan>knechte<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>stette<ex>n</ex></expan> vormals
